snippet.title: 观察者 Observer // Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2560250/Observer/

Observer is a 3D hand-drawn cartoon roguelite game. You will become the legendary heroes of the forest, choose a new destiny for them, and guard this mysterious forest for them.

Developed by Observer Studio
